<!DOCTYPE topic SYSTEM "mingle_help.dtd">
<topic title="Printing cards">
	<section title="Printing a single card">
		<p>In Mingle 2.3, we provide the ability to print a single card.</p>
		<p>Click on the 'Print' link from the action bar on a card view.</p>
			<screenshot alttext="single card print" src="resources/images/single_card_print_link.png"/>
			<p>The printed card includes</p>
			<bullets>
				<item>card number</item>
				<item>card title</item>
				<item>card version information</item>
				<item>all card description</item>
				<item>all properties and values</item>
				<item>card murmurs</item>
				<item>names of all attachments (if any)</item>
				<item>tags</item>
			</bullets>
	</section>
	
	<section title="Printing multiple cards" id="printing_from_card_list">
		<p>You can print multiple cards from the card list view.</p>
		<subsection file="card_printing_from_list_view" />
	</section>
	
	<bullets title="Also see...">
	   			<item><cref topic="list_view">List view</cref></item>
				<item><cref topic="card_view_page">Card view</cref></item>
	  </bullets>
</topic>
